The corpus contains 53 deep-loop gold labels with the old `sk-deep-*` IDs: 34 research and 19 review. That is enough to explain a large part of the drop, but not all of it, so I’m now running the actual scorer over the corpus and named P0s to split drift from genuine routing failures.
